_sText:
This map is a part of the j2 Abstract Mappack of 2008. It's the same style as the other ones: abstract/crazy/surreal.
There are a few spots where the displacements get a bit expensive on slower computers so I don't recommend playing this map on older machines. Most computers nowadays should be able to run this flawlessly though.

I'd like to thank everyone at the j2 forums for their help, support and advice and I'd like to thank them for letting me be a part of such a great mapping community.

Check out the zip's txt file for more info on the map.
Also check out the other maps in the abstract mappack!

Alpha's map seperately: 
http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/58218

And the whole pack:
http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/58046
